类 ChatterCreateGUI

ltseed.chatinmc.PlayerInteraction.GUI.SimpleGUI
ltseed.chatinmc.PlayerInteraction.GUI.FinalGUI.ChatterCreateGUI
所有已实现的接口:
org.bukkit.event.Listener
public class ChatterCreateGUI extends SimpleGUI
A GUI for creating a new Chatter. This GUI is used to gather information

from the player about the new Chatter that they want to create.

It extends SimpleGUI and is annotated with EnabledView.

版本:
1.0
作者:
LtSeed
